{"tid":2155854,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"保護傘人潮不再 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-08-14T05:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T09:22:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":96,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"b75067833501f7966fba1dc32a14686583dd791f","tid":2155854,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:16:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/PDQ3V7SA3ZA6NG75WDXQULDQK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FPDQ3V7SA3ZA6NG75WDXQULDQK4%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=4abfb519\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FPDQ3V7SA3ZA6NG75WDXQULDQK4%2F&h=0de20b1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/PDQ3V7SA3ZA6NG75WDXQULDQK4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n保護傘人潮不再 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4fLKgq5_eAohnOm2BSO5TaGnXGg=/775x517/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YRCND3DXFRDUNORBAWFRPTS7AY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4fLKgq5_eAohnOm2BSO5TaGnXGg%3D%2F775x517%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYRCND3DXFRDUNORBAWFRPTS7AY.jpg&h=3140d92d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎智英、周庭等人保釋得比我想像中快，不知是黨的善意，抑或別有顧慮。什麼顧慮？搞到肥佬黎「二度發達」事小，周庭引發全日本聲援事大。日本人看見嬌滴滴的「民主女神」被擒，舉國憤慨，同呼「放開個女仔佢」，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n群眾一剎那的激情，。。。。。。。。。。。這就是人類社會為什麼進步得這樣慢的原因。<br />\n<br />\n今天香港人支持蘋果的熱情，令世界動容，。。。。。。。。。。。。。但三個多月後又如何？<br />\n<br />\n似乎沒什麼人留意，保護傘的Facebook專頁已人間蒸發（大概跟「國安法」有關吧）。。。。。。。。。。。。現時顧客也以台灣人居多。香港人的三分鐘熱度，可見一斑。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。，蘋果日報也必須持續做得更好，才能真正留住讀者&mdash;&mdash;順帶溫馨提示一下，自從幾星期前蘋果更新系統，屢有年長讀者問我「名采版專欄去了哪裏」、「為什麼你每天文章的網址都停留在7月14日」等等，這些IT問題至今仍未修正。<br />\n<br />\n易經說：「不恆其德，或承之羞。」小至學習外語，大至改善社會，都有賴恆心；欠缺恆心，則往往以羞愧告終。請緊記：成就不是源自突如其來的衝動，而是依靠鍥而不捨的用功。"},{"pid":"61b516505bde09c3f00947cf9c7a10336efe30a5","tid":2155854,"uid":36510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:20:52.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"b896cabe01f3a089d5cdd57dc720a91982b1d7cc","tid":2155854,"uid":228894,"like":182,"dislike":1,"score":181,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:23:37.000Z","msg":"去唔到台灣點幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457ee48c4bcbdd2e5da0d65c0013dfad47380eba","tid":2155854,"uid":49643,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:25:54.000Z","msg":"在台港人幫手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e260fd6cab1b075987582f5131aceebb8749e4","tid":2155854,"uid":326017,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"b896cabe01f3a089d5cdd57dc720a91982b1d7cc","tid":2155854,"uid":228894,"like":182,"dislike":1,"score":181,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:23:37.000Z","msg":"去唔到台灣點幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:27:39.000Z","msg":"咪係<br />\n始終都要靠當地人"},{"pid":"cc153ea64b783fa4f53cc81e4e86e5d6c1ca51e9","tid":2155854,"uid":171684,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:28:05.000Z","msg":"香港人去唔到台灣旅行會唔會先係主因呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e80ba7720ca1c710442f058d509123581d62a8","tid":2155854,"uid":34409,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b896cabe01f3a089d5cdd57dc720a91982b1d7cc","tid":2155854,"uid":228894,"like":182,"dislike":1,"score":181,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:23:37.000Z","msg":"去唔到台灣點幫襯<img src=