去社企幫襯，因為覺得對社會有貢獻。但永遠無回頭客，幫襯都係一次起兩次止。所以好多社企都不斷改善經營手法，提升服務質素,令到生意持續發展。如果保護傘冇呢種mindset。相信都會步社企後塵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:39:45.000Z","msg":"有朋友不過去幫襯過，香港價錢，味道普通<br />\n<br />\n其實黃店、黃人，做咩都好，咬住啖氣做好佢<br />\n放啲心機落去做好件事，咪撚比人睇死<br />\n真香港人贏係贏轉數同幹勁，質素先會好過人<br />\n<br />\n如果做嘢求撚其，用咩拎出嚟贏支那人？"},{"pid":"e78ad5d8ec7e7c84f0b3c7e235a9b04d7ebd005c","tid":2155854,"uid":91897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bed7db30e4e503d5f576ace2d3746eac304ab3a","tid":2155854,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2c9bb7ac6c1bc6fcf06fe4489413b102d604d7d","tid":2155854,"uid":90521,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66fced4dcbee0e0addf7dbad2da2a40a5c52f756","tid":2155854,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現時顧客也以台灣人居多。香港人的三分鐘熱度，可見一斑。<br />\n<br />\n香港人點去台灣？唔靠當地人靠咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:42:21.000Z","msg":"一間鋪要靠外國人要撐到先大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:08:20.000Z","msg":"有咩問題，景點遊客都係外地人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:41:43.000Z","msg":"景點做遊客唔係問題, 但依家武肺搞到全世界旅遊業都收皮<br />\n唔係應該轉變下首先做番本地生意為主咩<br />\n再講...一個景點都係要由本地人多人去, 外地人先有興趣<br />\n都話香港人腦筋轉得快?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />收皮啦"},{"pid":"88465d02c2affd14d017cc22a17865352cfce5e8","tid":2155854,"uid":33618,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b896cabe01f3a089d5cdd57dc720a91982b1d7cc","tid":2155854,"uid":228894,"like":182,"dislike":1,"score":181,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:23:37.000Z","msg":"去唔到台灣點幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:42:02.000Z","msg":"咪係<br />\n我不知幾想去呀<br />\n同埋主力都係做本地人生意啦<br />\n又鬥黃"},{"pid":"ad90658356f1654874b813831ba46bf0e8b67837","tid":2155854,"uid":228525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:42:02.000Z","msg":"其實去到外國係咪應該更多靠實力而唔係感情"},{"pid":"cc0c0f0bdca14a564b2be14f8f237e0cdf42e858","tid":2155854,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:42:53.000Z","msg":"點撚樣去阿,on9?<br />\n同埋主要係台灣人食唔係好事咩"},{"pid":"9f9d4ba995b4ce74ccab45f663bf3b29500bba3c","tid":2155854,"uid":84511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad0309a20c8fe2eb56618bae17315fa873d5a7d3","tid":2155854,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb27227d44a136832a72c336f93499b47bb8b738","tid":2155854,"uid":362431,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:40:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:19:37.000Z","msg":"你實食撚過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:42:56.000Z","msg":"食過真心講，係勁撚難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8b8ccbb40df022b3e08cbde5effc30c070b219","tid":2155854,"uid":54371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:44:53.000Z","msg":"我都想去台灣<br />\n但而家去唔撚到嘛<br />\n個作者做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e24c95d6a7b31dcaf146fada07b9499aaaf0c2","tid":2155854,"uid":9254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:45:40.000Z","msg":"痴線，我係台灣讀書去過好多次，真係好難食。<br />\n而且一次難食過一次，真係改進下啦。<br />\n帶過我好多朋友去食，自己都覺得唔好意思。<br />\n價錢已經唔親民，食物質素仲咁低。"},{"pid":"9a19ad1fe7169b36ff90aa95ba8433d9977d494c","tid":2155854,"uid":237980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b75067833501f7966fba1dc32a14686583dd791f","tid":2155854,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:16:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/PDQ3V7SA3ZA6NG75WDXQULDQK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FPDQ3V7SA3ZA6NG75WDXQULDQK4%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=4abfb519\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FPDQ3V7SA3ZA6NG75WDXQULDQK4%2F&h=0de20b1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/PDQ3V7SA3ZA6NG75WDXQULDQK4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n保護傘人潮不再 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4fLKgq5_eAohnOm2BSO5TaGnXGg=/775x517/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YRCND3DXFRDUNORBAWFRPTS7AY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4fLKgq5_eAohnOm2BSO5TaGnXGg%3D%2F775x517%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYRCND3DXFRDUNORBAWFRPTS7AY.jpg&h=3140d92d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎智英、周庭等人保釋得比我想像中快，不知是黨的善意，抑或別有顧慮。什麼顧慮？搞到肥佬黎「二度發達」事小，周庭引發全日本聲援事大。日本人看見嬌滴滴的「民主女神」被擒，舉國憤慨，同呼「放開個女仔佢」，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n群眾一剎那的激情，。。。。。。。。。。。這就是人類社會為什麼進步得這樣慢的原因。<br />\n<br />\n今天香港人支持蘋果的熱情，令世界動容，。。。。。。。。。。。。。但三個多月後又如何？<br />\n<br />\n似乎沒什麼人留意，保護傘的Facebook專頁已人間蒸發（大概跟「國安法」有關吧）。。。。。。。。。。。。現時顧客也以台灣人居多。香港人的三分鐘熱度，可見一斑。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。，蘋果日報也必須持續做得更好，才能真正留住讀者&mdash;&mdash;順帶溫馨提示一下，自從幾星期前蘋果更新系統，屢有年長讀者問我「名采版專欄去了哪裏」、「為什麼你每天文章的網址都停留在7月14日」等等，這些IT問題至今仍未修正。<br />\n<br />\n易經說：「不恆其德，或承之羞。」小至學習外語，大至改善社會，都有賴恆心；欠缺恆心，則往往以羞愧告終。請緊記：成就不是源自突如其來的衝動，而是依靠鍥而不捨的用功。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:51:30.000Z","msg":"朋友留學台灣，有次專程走去食<br />\n<br />\n食評如下: 港幣價錢(TWD120~140一碟意粉) 港式份量 自助服務(得一個樓面) AND 佢等左有半個鐘先有野食 野係好食但同價隔離鋪無論份量服務時間都屌打 <br />\n我就問一句憑咩 黃唔係大撚哂 連符合當地水平同一間食店既要求既做唔到，真係靠愛及電"},{"pid":"7f2ef1e9c02d23e5fa1eab0ce5f933d1d51af727","tid":2155854,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75e24c95d6a7b31dcaf146fada07b9499aaaf0c2","tid":2155854,"uid":9254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:45:40.000Z","msg":"痴線，我係台灣讀書去過好多次，真係好難食。<br />\n而且一次難食過一次，真係改進下啦。<br />\n帶過我好多朋友去食，自己都覺得唔好意思。<br />\n價錢已經唔親民，食物質素仲咁低。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:52:54.000Z","msg":"台灣對大件夾抵食要求好高"},{"pid":"917b859295013bd75c42488bc65723b18bb6a84e","tid":2155854,"uid":270214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:54:37.000Z","msg":"佢自己餐廳除咗做食都要出多d橋嚟吸客<br />\n尤其喺台灣嘅外國人，順便做國際線<br />\n<br />\n唔好成日旨意塘水滾塘魚"},{"pid":"c012b95566a3379f0095bca0849638028439b978","tid":2155854,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:56:13.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"af98df866a617675c09522343021a0895b5e9778","tid":2155854,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:56:37.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"935d470d95a5b8b30324209e7870e63dab50435f","tid":2155854,"uid":237980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a19ad1fe7169b36ff90aa95ba8433d9977d494c","tid":2155854,"uid":237980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b75067833501f7966fba1dc32a14686583dd791f","tid":2155854,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:16:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/PDQ3V7SA3ZA6NG75WDXQULDQK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FPDQ3V7SA3ZA6NG75WDXQULDQK4%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=4abfb519\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FPDQ3V7SA3ZA6