%2FKKY0jf9.jpg&h=fbfd598c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66a5c7db95e21110e24c038616e0048a36b95be2","tid":2155854,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b896cabe01f3a089d5cdd57dc720a91982b1d7cc","tid":2155854,"uid":228894,"like":182,"dislike":1,"score":181,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:23:37.000Z","msg":"去唔到台灣點幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:02:39.000Z","msg":"其實之前有post講過，間野d野食唔掂，始終都係在台港人用熱情去撐<br />\n老實講 保護傘意念好好，但有d野始終要用番商業模式去run<br />\n<br />\n希望佢地遲d搞果檔野可以認真諗吓"},{"pid":"d424b31c67ea2175ab1d92f13579fbfdf7acc994","tid":2155854,"uid":96465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:04:48.000Z","msg":"對唔撚住 洗唔洗即刻坐大飛去食"},{"pid":"b0f1430d398309f9f86a8843f8836280bf1384b3","tid":2155854,"uid":9254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f2ef1e9c02d23e5fa1eab0ce5f933d1d51af727","tid":2155854,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75e24c95d6a7b31dcaf146fada07b9499aaaf0c2","tid":2155854,"uid":9254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:45:40.000Z","msg":"痴線，我係台灣讀書去過好多次，真係好難食。<br />\n而且一次難食過一次，真係改進下啦。<br />\n帶過我好多朋友去食，自己都覺得唔好意思。<br />\n價錢已經唔親民，食物質素仲咁低。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:52:54.000Z","msg":"台灣對大件夾抵食要求好高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:19:04.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦，公館係台大站，基本上都係有錢子弟<br />\n吾關大吾大件抵吾抵食。係好撚難食"},{"pid":"3b11c84d8609a614518be3bf8504acc61129a053","tid":2155854,"uid":251660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:45:01.000Z","msg":"野唔好食 又貴<br />\n你唔做好啲點吸引當地人幫襯"},{"pid":"5bce6f307bf95a91a2ba39753e6150ca42282822","tid":2155854,"uid":81005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"556be9ed56959d85a265fcaf5bdeb15483964d78","tid":2155854,"uid":90521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"64f5cfe1bb595e189b7368e812c9a03cef5d83f9","tid":2155854,"uid":141879,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:46:49.000Z","msg":"其實保護傘既處竟同普通社企餐廳面對既一樣。一開張好多人去社企幫襯，因為覺得對社會有貢獻。但永遠無回頭客，幫襯都係一次起兩次止。所以好多社企都不斷改善經營手法，提升服務質素,令到生意持續發展。如果保護傘冇呢種mindset。相信都會步社企後塵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:56:41.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n一間餐廳最緊要就係野好食先吸引到人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:58:06.000Z","msg":"其實一開頭保護傘既background已經為佢地間餐廳吸引左好多客源，須知唔係間間餐廳都咁好彩。如果留唔住，只能怪餐廳質素。要努力呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80446e8f0482b4ca35c9114a9c89205a6e52694","tid":2155854,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T08:17:12.000Z","msg":"如果可旅行<br />\n每20港人有一個幫襯佢地生意已經穩定"},{"pid":"9c377ef3cf2ccefc157ba4f579011afefd78af26","tid":2155854,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2e0e32520e0c868a79393f86bbd04bce4c4f369","tid":2155854,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:11:13.000Z","msg":"咪鬥黃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三個月後買唔買蘋果都要比你批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T08:23:45.000Z","msg":"你有冇睇過篇文<br />\n篇野冇怪責過消費者，只係講做生意唔可以靠黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7596ba2ee27ebef1871ac4685719be2a99892bff","tid":2155854,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T08:24:03.000Z","msg":"直接開個眾籌啦，我即刻俾，OK?"}]}